{"tid":383515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：《國歌法》刑罰應最高監禁3年    遠高於支那行政拘留15日","createTime":"2017-09-01T14:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T00:38:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93cb60f52f449668a508d67b7fc4a160ed413b88","tid":383515,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170901004025-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170901004025-260409&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=dfdce05f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170901004025-260409</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸9月1日正式通過《國歌法》，將於10月1日起施行，新法規定國歌不得在私人喪事活動等不適宜場合使用 中小學也應將國歌作為愛國主義教育的重要內容；若故意篡改國歌歌詞、曲譜，以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，將被公安機關處以警告或者十五日以下拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1648139/楊岳橋%3A政府須在《國歌法》釐清違法行為\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1648139%2F%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B%253A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%88%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=0331e8ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1648139/楊岳橋%3A政府須在《國歌法》釐清違法行為</a><br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬認為，《國歌法》為市民提供清晰的指引，未來本地立法的過程，應該和過去《國旗法》和《國徽法》類似，最高罰款可能是5萬元，監禁3年。"},{"pid":"8fffe426d40e7b01a6bf8d47cfba1734ce845f15","tid":383515,"uid":38194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"香港真係玩撚完"},{"pid":"b58f4146246009f54cba77a6a7a4326f35f3f6ca","tid":383515,"uid":29804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"起來 我帶你去環遊世界"},{"pid":"1df1ed3034a39830f3d4ff3bcfaf7ea1b09eb7d4","tid":383515,"uid":9825,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:24:00.000Z"